519
01:15:56,643 --> 01:15:59,145
Isto?

520
01:16:01,013 --> 01:16:02,615
É azul?

521
01:16:03,716 --> 01:16:07,186
O mar? Não sei.

522
01:16:08,287 --> 01:16:10,089
Antes era.

523
01:16:37,750 --> 01:16:38,952
Espera.

524
01:16:56,302 --> 01:16:58,638
